cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e【The IGOGOMI Fold】All the benefits of an E-bike has packed into the original 3-part fold. It takes around 25-seconds to transform your bike into a small compact package (26 ×  13  × 28.7 inches )（L × W × H）,that you can tow, stow and carry anywhere. Travels on rush-hour trains, metros, underground, overground, car trunks, and cabs. There is no need to leave it outside. Just enjoy the ride\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e【Your ride, You decide】 Customize your ride performance with 3 riding modes. Go full throttle up to 19 mile/h on battery power alone. But the IGOGOMI folding bike also rides like a traditional pedal-only bicycle. Need some extra oomph? Turn on the pedal-to-go for a boost of electric power as you pedal. It simplifies the riding experience for you.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e【Charge on the go】The compact IGOGOMI Electric 36V / 6.8Ah lithium-ion battery packs in the power. The range is 25-35miles. Charging it is just as simple as plugging in your phone. Plug into any standard outlet and fully charge in 4 hours. \u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e【The IGOGOMI Fold】All the benefits of an E-bike has packed into the original 3-part fold. It takes around 25-seconds to transform your bike into a small compact package (26 ×  13  × 28.7 inches )（L × W × H）,that you can tow, stow and carry anywhere. Travels on rush-hour trains, metros, underground, overground, car trunks, and cabs. There is no need to leave it outside. Just enjoy the ride\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e【Your ride, You decide】 Customize your ride performance with 3 riding modes. Go full throttle up to 19 mile/h on battery power alone. But the IGOGOMI folding bike also rides like a traditional pedal-only bicycle. Need some extra oomph? Turn on the pedal-to-go for a boost of electric power as you pedal. It simplifies the riding experience for you.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e【Charge on the go】The compact IGOGOMI Electric 36V / 6.8Ah lithium-ion battery packs in the power. The range is 25-35miles. Charging it is just as simple as plugging in your phone. Plug into any standard outlet and fully charge in 4 hours. \u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},"type":"text"}},"settings":{"background_color":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","desktop_media_width":56,"heading_color":"","media_enable_video_autoplay":false,"media_enable_video_looping":true,"media_fit_height":true,"media_layout_desktop":"carousel_vertical","media_mobile_indicator":"thumbnails","media_size":"","media_zoom":"lightbox","show_breadcrumbs":false,"show_sticky_add_to_cart":true,"sticky_add_to_cart_position":"right","text_color":""},"type":"main-product"},"main-details":{"block_order":["5bbfd876-e943-47d3-b984-06f967dfd314","096eee3c-a9d6-48a0-b676-2f8ecf38fe75"],"blocks":{"096eee3c-a9d6-48a0-b676-2f8ecf38fe75":{"disabled":true,"settings":{"collapse_open":false,"content":"\u003cp\u003eProvide your customers with additional information about the product.\u003c/p\u003e","heading":"Collapsible content"},"type":"collapsible_content"},"5bbfd876-e943-47d3-b984-06f967dfd314":{"disabled":true,"settings":{"collapse_content":true,"collapse_open":true,"heading":""},"type":"description"}},"settings":{},"type":"main-product-details"},"related-products":{"settings":{"background_color":"","carousel":true,"content":"","full_width":true,"grid_columns":4,"grid_columns_mobile":"2","heading":"You may also like","heading_color":"","heading_size":"h2","products_count":8,"subheading":"","text_alignment":"text-center","text_color":""},"type":"related-products"}}}